%%{init: {"theme": "base", "themeVariables": {"fontFamily": "Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui", "background": "#0B1020", "primaryColor": "#E0F2FE", "primaryBorderColor": "#38BDF8", "primaryTextColor": "#0F172A", "actorBkg": "#E0F2FE", "actorBorder": "#0284C7", "actorTextColor": "#0F172A", "activationBkgColor": "#FEF3C7", "activationBorderColor": "#D97706", "sequenceNumberColor": "#FFFFFF", "lineColor": "#94A3B8", "noteBkgColor": "#DCFCE7", "noteTextColor": "#0F172A", "noteBorderColor": "#16A34A"}, "sequence": {"showSequenceNumbers": true, "mirrorActors": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Worker as 🤖 Worker
  participant Proposal as 📦 Proposal bundle
  participant Safety as 🛡️ Safety gate
  participant Human as 👤 Dmitry approval
  participant Backup as 🧰 Backup plan
  participant Vault as 🗄️ Vault / sandbox
  participant Verify as 🔎 Fresh verify
  participant Report as 🧾 Report

  Worker->>Proposal: emit proposal.json + proposal.md only
  Note over Worker,Proposal: dry-run default • evidence • risk • target list
  Proposal->>Safety: validate protected paths and output location
  alt unsafe path / missing evidence / no approval phrase
    Safety-->>Worker: refuse with issues[]
    Worker->>Report: write failure evidence
  else safe proposal
    Safety->>Human: request explicit approval phrase
    alt no approval
      Human-->>Report: pending / rejected decision
    else approved
      Human->>Backup: approve narrow target set
      Backup->>Vault: create scoped backup before apply
      Vault->>Vault: apply approved targets only
      Vault->>Verify: run fresh observe + compare
      Verify-->>Report: PASS/FAIL with commands and artifacts
    end
  end
